Package: rtemis.llm
Title: LLMs and Agentic AI
Version: 0.7.2
Date: 2026-04-21
Authors@R: person(given = "E.D.", family = "Gennatas", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), 
    email = "gennatas@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9280-3609"))
Description: Provides an Agent class with support for reasoning, structured output, memory 
    management, and tool use. Allows creation of custom LLM-based workflows and agentic AI systems 
    using a functional user-facing frontend and an 'S7' backend. Includes llmapply() for quick batch
    LLM inference. Supports 'Ollama', 'OpenAI'-compatible, and 'Anthropic'-compatible endpoints.
